<h2>3. McGee Run to Bemis </h2>
<table class='data_table river-stats'>
<tr class='row-1'>
<th>Usual Difficulty</th>
<td>III-V (for normal flows) </td>
</tr>
<tr class='row-2'>
<th>Length</th>
<td>13 Miles </td>
</tr>
</table>
